title: American horror story asylum - Anne franks back story/ the truth about doctor Arden
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: The only show that can get away with having Anne Frank, evil Santa, a possessed nun, and aliens, all in one season.
Fun Fact: The actor who played Dr. Arden had a real life son that was so identical to him, he got to play him in the Nazi flashbacks.
Bruh this ended up being one hell of a coincidence. The Anne Frank lady turned out to be crazy, but Arden was FOR REAL a Nazi. But nobody believed her. What are the odds 😂
The whole Anne Frank episodes were crazy!
they picked the perfect person to play young dr. Arden, they look JUST alike
